            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "You've improved quite a bit at Synthesis, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh, really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Unlike at first, I feel at ease watching you now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ehehe, I'm glad about that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "It may be about time for you to try challenging yourself with Synthesis that isn't restricted by recipes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Do you mean I should ignore the recipes? I wonder if that would be okay..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "No, you wouldn't completely ignore the recipes. You would simply devise new ways to use them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "For example, you could change the recipes you currently have by adding one more item."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I see... Maybe I'll try that?"
        }
    ]
}